Package: RASCO
Type: Package
Title: An R Package to Alleviate Spatial Confounding
Version: 0.0.3
Author: Douglas R. M. Azevedo
Maintainer: Douglas R. M. Azevedo <douglasrm.azevedo@gmail.com>
Description: This package allow the application of several restricted models for
    generalized linear regressions and survival analysis under spatial confounding.
